There are many ways you can contribute to LDTP !

 * ["Download"] LDTP and install them
 * Report ["Bugs"] when you found them
 * Submit patches

There are many exciting (new) projects that you can contribute to:

 * Help us to improve the Website
 * Write / Improve [wiki:Docs documentation]
 * Write test scripts for [http://www.gnome.org GNOME] / [http://www.mozilla.org Mozilla] using ["Testcases"]
 * Improve LDTP recording
 * Improve LDTP engine performance
